name: Keys_Running
description:
🕹Get the three keys before the time over and without being hit by the obstacles!

Think you can do that? lets see!

---------------------------------------------

🎮How to play: 

Press right arrow to move right.

Press left arrow to move left.

Press up arrow to jump.

Press space to slide.
